It's still a fun and eclectic store, filled with surprising and sometimes weird items.  Last night, I spent most my time marveling at the large and "unique" ugly Christmas sweater selection.  Ohhh boy, there's a lot of them in stock at Spencer's right now.

It's a fun store, prices are good, and the product lines are unique and different.
